{"tid":2086355,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"警方批襲擊律師陳子遷者喪心病狂毫無人性","createTime":"2020-06-30T08:56:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-30T09:04:18.000Z","uid":277339,"like":2,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"4b31f885b7c5753e66569c70b18c648de7f7af2f","tid":2086355,"uid":277339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T08:56:01.000Z","msg":"30.06.2020 16:50<br />\n警方拘捕6名男子，懷疑和上月律師會成員陳子遷在銅鑼灣遇襲有關，他們涉嫌傷人和非法集結被捕，年齡介乎15至32歲，報稱是學生、送貨員和無業。<br />\n<br />\n警方表示，陳子遷當日不憤暴徒的行為，出言阻止，但暴徒不單沒有停止，至少20人對他拳打腳踢，還用鐵枝和雨傘等硬物施襲，形容他們喪心病狂、毫無人性，同時有人打開雨傘作掩護，最終陳子遷身體多處受傷，要縫20多針。警方又譴責有人鼓吹、美化和縱容暴力，指他們是「殺君馬者道旁兒」，行為本身不單違法，還鼓勵其他人施襲，形成不良的社會氛圍，削弱市民的守法意識。<br />\n<br />\n所以點解斬人藍絲係情操高尚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1324997&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1324997%26csid%3D261_341&d=r9GgQvVcrWtMp%2Fshn5VX%2F7%2FszHQdc4%2B4ddc640yZrNs%3D&h=e41a7411\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1324997&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"b76f36234c5aa29bb5805fca1eb5272bda907ca5","tid":2086355,"uid":121197,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T08:59:12.000Z","msg":"佢唔出現喺嗰度咪無事"},{"pid":"a14294561057d8b14c65a2931f7d61643e86059b","tid":2086355,"uid":34410,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T08:59:37.000Z","msg":"驚咪唔好出街囉"},{"pid":"c15114b1634cbe6dfef9c12402b7023d52619577","tid":2086355,"uid":2267,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b76f36234c5aa29bb5805fca1eb5272bda907ca5","tid":2086355,"uid":121197,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T08:59:12.000Z","msg":"佢唔出現喺嗰度咪無事"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T08:59:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pOdkZWe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpOd